➜宽哥：《又别老屋》
http://www.sohu.com/a/423203096_100115135	16176
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201008/94665e0bae404644a5b312f5e1c189f9.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《又别老屋》—平水韵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寒风落日满残霞，古巷轻烟缭旧家。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夜半挑灯犹似昨，故乡不觉是天涯。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201008/1a317a1c231944dda192ec17a2b873d6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201008/61809c0b9d9b444f95fd1c43dbde4a7d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
